<C>__{abby}
<D>__{maybe i should eat the worm.}
<A>__{ken looks over.}
<C>__{ken}
<D>__{is mike alexander the guy you went on the date with?}
<C>__{abby}
<D>__{no, that was a different source of humiliation, but thank you for reminding me.}
