<D>__{i still don't understand why you didn't just marry bill. he was a good guy.}
<C>__{abby}
<D>__{yeah...he was. but he also had navy blue sheets and bath towels with tassels. he played computer games on his phone. he wore open toed shoes. sometimes with socks. and his mother called him "bucky".}
